---
layout: base.njk
title: "Blog"
siteName: "Il Grimorio"
breadcrumb: "Blog"
---

<h1>Blog</h1>

<p><em>Note, aggiornamenti e riflessioni dal master.</em></p>

{% if collections.blog and collections.blog.length %}
<ul class="entry-list">
{% for item in collections.blog %}
  <li>
    <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
    {% if item.data.date %}<div class="entry-meta">{{ item.data.date | readableDate }}{% if item.data.description %} — {{ item.data.description }}{% endif %}</div>{% endif %}
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
<p><em>Nessun articolo ancora presente.</em></p>
{% endif %}
